Table oms.ExecutionBeanKeyDefDO (Enum)

Execution bean keys are additional configurable properties that are used from {@link ExecutionBeanDefDO}.
Customer e-mails for example use at least the property keys "shopEmailAddress" and "messageTemplate" (ExecutionBeanDefDO is SHOP_CUSTOMER_MAIL_SENDER).
